One of the features that make Semantic Chapter useful is the ability to create interactive elements like quizzes and exercises. These interactive elements can help engage readers and enhance their learning experience. Another feature that I find useful is the ability to create a table of contents that can be used for navigation within the document. This helps readers quickly find the information they need and allows them to jump to different sections of the document easily. Overall, Semantic Chapter is a powerful tool that can be used to create well-structured and interactive documents, which can be especially useful for educational or instructional materials.
